data.description: Beautiful waterfront property located off of the Little Manatee River. This adorable home features 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths and has been completely renovated over the years. Updated metal roof, impact windows, waterproof laminate, new AC in 2017 and more. Even better, there's no HOA or CDD so you can park your boat or RV under the large cover and enjoy watching the dolphins on the custom deck. You can see the pride of ownership as you walk through this well kept, light and bright home and the owners did a pre-listing inspection so you can be sure you're getting a home that is in tip top shape. Seller is also providing a home warranty. Call for your private showing.
